00:05:11.221 --> 00:05:13.686
Round and thin,
originally from France

00:05:13.911 --> 00:05:19.014
A baked delicacy
with a waffle-like uneven texture

00:05:19.181 --> 00:05:23.919
I loved it so much, yet I couldn't even 
remember the name right away

00:05:24.189 --> 00:05:30.513
Maybe I'm blocking it out, 
so it won't remind me of you

00:05:32.891 --> 00:05:36.431
One, two... Go!

00:05:37.544 --> 00:05:42.144
We wish that this manuscript be accepted!

00:05:42.396 --> 00:05:43.419
Wanna go home?

00:05:43.442 --> 00:05:44.697
Let's go!

00:05:46.478 --> 00:05:48.053
Where should we go today?

00:05:48.053 --> 00:05:50.893
Haruyo's place!

00:05:52.201 --> 00:05:53.379
Good idea!

00:05:53.467 --> 00:05:54.616
It's a bit chilly today.

00:05:54.812 --> 00:05:57.383
It is! I don't wanna be outside!

00:05:57.806 --> 00:05:59.558
Let's have fun! Got any new games?